Author: Kristof Keppens <kkeppens@gmail.com>
Date:   Mon Jul 19 16:35:40 2021 +0200

    Prevent search service endpoint from querying series service
    
    This patch fixes the problem that the search service's episode endpoint uses the series service when providing the `sname` parameter. Instead of relying on the series service, we can use the Solr search index directly to map the `sname` parameter to a series identifier.
    
    This fixes #2738
